i.png?m=1602814922","location":"","btc":null,"id":509050},"last_reply_by":"dongcxcx","last_touched":1626869161,"title":"周末团建你怎么看？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790875","created":1626855829,"content":"下周公司组织团建，日期定在下周末。真不想去","content_rendered":"<p>下周公司组织团建，日期定在下周末。真不想去</p>\n","last_modified":1626855829,"replies":14,"id":790875},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1626622970","name":"android","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1626622970","title":"Android","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","topics":8871,"footer":"","header":"来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。","title_alternative":"Android","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1626622970","stars":4845,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":39,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"username":"3dwelcome","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2d0/2f32/162136_mini.png?m=1617116799","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/3dwelcome","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1457260101,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2d0/2f32/162136_mini.png?m=1617116799","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d2d0/2f32/162136_mini.png?m=1617116799","location":"","btc":"","id":162136},"last_reply_by":"araraloren","last_touched":1626850916,"title":"安卓开发小技巧，教你们如何用文本 XML 动态生成界面。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790800","created":1626838874,"content":"第一步，运行时动态下载 Layout XML 文件，用 binxml 之类的工具函数，转换成 Byte[]类型的二进制 XML （模仿 AndroidStudio 的资源编译流程）\r\n\r\n第二步，把每个按钮的资源 ID 包名赋值一下，因为动态载入 Layout 的 JAVA 函数，会自动去 resources.arsc 资源列表查找对应的 ID，而按钮是动态生成的，根本就没有 ID，需要随便分配一个，只要当前 View 内不重复即可。\r\n\r\n第三步，用 LayoutInflater.inflate 和老外写的 XmlBlock 内部资源解析函数，正式加载二进制 XML 界面，转换成 View 组件。( https://github.com/liudongmiao/preference-fragment-compat/blob/master/src/me/piebridge/android/preference/PreferenceFragment.java#L235 )\r\n\r\n第四步，用 findViewById 查找按钮的 view, 用 setOnClickListener 设置响应事件，setContentView 显示出来，搞定收工。","content_rendered":"<p>第一步，运行时动态下载 Layout XML 文件，用 binxml 之类的工具函数，转换成 Byte[]类型的二进制 XML （模仿 AndroidStudio 的资源编译流程）</p>\n<p>第二步，把每个按钮的资源 ID 包名赋值一下，因为动态载入 Layout 的 JAVA 函数，会自动去 resources.arsc 资源列表查找对应的 ID，而按钮是动态生成的，根本就没有 ID，需要随便分配一个，只要当前 View 内不重复即可。</p>\n<p>第三步，用 LayoutInflater.inflate 和老外写的 XmlBlock 内部资源解析函数，正式加载二进制 XML 界面，转换成 View 组件。( <a href=\"https://github.com/liudongmiao/preference-fragment-compat/blob/master/src/me/piebridge/android/preference/PreferenceFragment.java#L235\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/liudongmiao/preference-fragment-compat/blob/master/src/me/piebridge/android/preference/PreferenceFragment.java#L235</a> )</p>\n<p>第四步，用 findViewById 查找按钮的 view, 用 setOnClickListener 设置响应事件，setContentView 显示出来，搞定收工。</p>\n","last_modified":1626838874,"replies":14,"id":790800},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1615111905","name":"iphone","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1615111905","title":"iPhone","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":8623,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":"iPhone","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1615111905","stars":2690,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":8,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"username":"hfl1995","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/35bf/bde0/161110_mini.png?m=1596591308","bio":"数码爱好者","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hfl1995","tagline":"没有签名","twitter":"","created":1456738283,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/35bf/bde0/161110_mini.png?m=1596591308","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/35bf/bde0/161110_mini.png?m=1596591308","location":"北京朝阳","btc":"","id":161110},"last_reply_by":"dingwen07","last_touched":1626843577,"title":"iPhoneX 忘记锁屏密码，刷机的时候卡进度条怎么办","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790779","created":1626834907,"content":"如题，卡住不动了","content_rendered":"<p>如题，卡住不动了</